			    		<h3>Here are the "Golden Rules" that you must qualify for to obtain active trader status.</h3>
			    		<h5>
			    			<ul>
			    				<li>Trade full-time or part-time, all day, every day.</li>
			    				<li>Minimum 4 hours per day, average, working your trading business.</li>
			    				<li>No real lapses in activity. You trade all year long, like youâ€™re working a full-time job.</li>
			    				<li>Trade on 75 percent or more of available trading days.</li>
			    				<li>You should be making 1,000 trades or more each year.</li>
			    				<li>Most of your trades should be day or swing trades</li>
			    				<li>Your demonstrated intent should be to make a living as a trader.</li>
			    				<li>You have invested heavily in tools, education, software, etc.</li>
